    h1 Typography
    ul.docs-index
    p Framework7 comes with a lot of additional CSS helper classes to help you with extra styling and formatting.
    h2 Content Spacing
    h3 Margin
    table.methods-table
      tbody
        tr
          th(colspan="2") Margin
        tr
          td margin
